Package: semFromKeys
Type: Package
Title: Run Structural Equation lavaan Models from Keys Lists
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Timothy F.", "Bainbridge",
      email = "tfbainbridge@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Specifying lavaan models manually can be time consuming when
    multiple similar models are required. The semFromKeys package aims to
    streamline the process of running lavaan models by generating model code
    from simple keys lists instead of writing out model code manually.
    The package also checks that identical models have not been run on the same
    data, which saves time when code needs to be run again or when some upstream
    changes may have changed model code or data.
